    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[1].lines.Array.size
      value: 12
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[2].lines.Array.size
      value: 8
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[3].lines.Array.size
      value: 12
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[4].lines.Array.size
      value: 3
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[0]
      value: Technician's Log, March 8th -
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[1]
      value: It has something to do with the transmitter
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[2]
      value: Every time I think I've found the right frequency it...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[3]
      value: It's not right. This place is not right
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[4]
      value: 'The steps are always the same:'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[5]
      value: 1. Configure the antenna
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[6]
      value: 2. Find the frequency
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[7]
      value: 3. Tune the radio
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[8]
      value: Then the other door will open...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[9]
      value: Then the other door will open
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[0]
      value: 'Technician''s Log, June 26th - '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[1]
      value: It's different this time
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[2]
      value: Every loop, the world just feels like its... falling apart
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[3]
      value: Whatever this place is supposed to be, it's breaking down
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[4]
      value: There's something else here with me
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[5]
      value: Something in the static...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[6]
      value: I've seen it out of the corner of my eye
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[7]
      value: It's so tall. I don't know if its seen me, though
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[8]
      value: I just need to keep going
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[9]
      value: The steps are the same as before
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[0]
      value: 'Technician''s Log - '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[1]
      value: I can hear it watching me through the walls
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[2]
      value: Watching me go through these cycles over and over again
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[3]
      value: I KNOW YOU CAN SEE ME!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[4]
      value: It's falling apart... I can feel it
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[5]
      value: I'm falling apart...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[6]
      value: Just one more loop
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[7]
      value: Just one more time through the door...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[8]
      value: Just one more time through the door...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[0]
      value: Technician...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[1]
      value: Just one more loop...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[2]
      value: Just one more...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[3]
      value: Just one...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[4]
      value: Just...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[5]
      value: ...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[6]
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[7]
      value: There is an... observer
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[8]
      value: You... must leave
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[9]
      value: The door...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[4].lines.Array.data[0]
      value: Cycle 4
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[4].lines.Array.data[1]
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[4].lines.Array.data[2]
      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[10]
      value: They're always the same
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[11]
      value: I just need to make it through the door...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[10]
      value: Through the door...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5882105566044553854, guid: a145678c6ae9845b9a71495a4d9ed516, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueObjs.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[11]
      value: Once more... beyond the door
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
